    "Memory footprint (MB)" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "メモリフットプリント（MB）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CPU — app total, % of one core" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CPU — アプリ合計（1コア比 %）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Screen load (frame supply)" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "画面負荷（フレーム供給）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Off (static)" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オフ（静止）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Light" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "軽"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Heavy" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "重"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "static — no frames for ReplayKit" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "静止 — ReplayKit にフレームは流れません"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ReplayKit only delivers frames while the screen changes — a static screen costs almost nothing. Heavy redraws a full-width canvas every frame ≒ worst case while recording." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ReplayKit は画面に変化があるときだけフレームを供給します。静止画面のコストはほぼゼロ。「重」は毎フレーム全面を再描画 ≒ 録画中の最悪ケースです。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "How to read the numbers" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "数値の読み方"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Memory: ring segments live on disk, not in RAM — the recording delta is roughly the encoder session and stays flat over time." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• メモリ: リングのセグメントは RAM ではなくディスク上。録画中の増分はおおむねエンコーダセッション分で、時間が経っても増えません。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Ring on disk: plateaus at the retention window (the ring drops old segments) — an hour of recording stores no more than the last N seconds." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• リング（ディスク）: 保持窓で頭打ちになります（古いセグメントは順次破棄）。1時間録画しても保存されるのは直近 N 秒分だけです。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• CPU: frame capture runs in replayd (out of process). What you see here is the in-process cost: sample callbacks + the hardware H.264 encoder." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• CPU: フレームキャプチャ自体は replayd（プロセス外）で動きます。ここに出るのはアプリ内コスト＝サンプルコールバック＋ハードウェア H.264 エンコーダ分です。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Frame pacing: spikes in the worst frame gap while recording would indicate UI jank caused by the SDK." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• フレームペーシング: 録画中に最大フレームギャップが跳ねる場合、SDK 起因の UI カクつきを意味します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "thermal: nominal" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "発熱: 正常"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "thermal: fair" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "発熱: やや上昇"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "thermal: serious" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "発熱: 高"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "thermal: critical" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "発熱: 危険"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Reset" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "リセット"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Export CSV" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "CSVを書き出す"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Soak comparison (answering \"what does it cost?\")" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "放置比較（「結局いくらかかるの？」に答える）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Fix the load, tap reset, leave it ~10 min with recording OFF, export the CSV. Then turn recording ON, reset, and repeat. The ON−OFF delta is the SDK's net cost." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 負荷を固定 → リセット → 録画 OFF のまま約10分放置 → CSV を書き出し。次に録画 ON にしてリセットし、同じことを繰り返します。ON と OFF の差分が SDK の正味コストです。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Auto-lock is disabled while this panel is visible, so unattended soaks keep running." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• このパネル表示中は画面の自動ロックを無効化するので、放置計測が途切れません。"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "version" : "1.0"
}
